//! MediaProcessing flow implementation
//!
//! Generated by metaphor-schema
//!
//! Asynchronous media processing workflow triggered after a file is uploaded.
//! Generates thumbnails and previews for images, videos, and documents.
//! Reusable by any upload flow that emits FileUploadedEvent.

